      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the shim-and-bucket valve clearances were recently calibrated to factory specifications. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the chassis dynamics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and a linear power delivery that pulls cleanly to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
